## Database Configuration

```sql
-- Set statement timeout per role (prevents runaway queries)
ALTER ROLE authenticated SET statement_timeout = '10s';
ALTER ROLE anon SET statement_timeout = '5s';

-- Increase work_mem for complex sorts/joins (default 4MB is low)
ALTER ROLE authenticated SET work_mem = '32MB';

-- Check current settings
SHOW statement_timeout;
SHOW work_mem;
SHOW max_connections;

-- View all custom role settings
SELECT rolname, rolconfig FROM pg_roles WHERE rolconfig IS NOT NULL;
```

