## Stale Statistics Fix

If EXPLAIN shows huge mismatch between estimated and actual rows:
```sql
-- Update statistics for one table
ANALYZE orders;

-- Update all tables
ANALYZE;

-- Auto-analyze is usually on, but for large bulk imports run manually
```
